Code is keep in branch [sfence_hades_revisited](https://github.com/sfence/travelnet/tree/sfence_hades_revisited).

This is modified version of mod [travelnet](https://content.minetest.net/packages/mt-mods/travelnet/)
 from [Sokomine](https://content.minetest.net/users/Sokomine/), now mantained by mt-mods.

title: Travelnet for Hades Revisited
